description:
Sardinia

Travel Documentary hosted by Anthony Bourdain, published by Discovery Channel broadcasted as part of DC No Reservations series in 2009 - English narration


Information
------------------------------

Tony visits Sardinia, his wife's homeland, and gets a lesson in what it means to be Sardinian. Tony learns that Sardinia really is its own country with a strong island mentality.

